node.text:
•

F.E.A.R= Finally, Exiting, Average, Reality
•

In order for us to tap into that next orbit of our lives, we have to leave the fear behind.
•

Fear keeps us average, and i’ll be honest.. You are Extrodinary in so many aspects of your life.
•

But you’ll never tap in because you’re choosing F.E.A.R
•

You’ve become accustomed to not living on your higher self.
•

If a eagle lived with chickens, he’d accept the fact that he couldn’t soar.
•

It’s time for you to soar, it’s time for you to over come F.E.A.R.
•

It’s Time for you to live the life you Want.
•

WALLSTREET LOOKS LIKE US NOW

node.title: I Will No Longer Fertilize My Fears

THE BEST OF BOTH WORLDS!!

Leaders Lead Everyday, Not just when it’s convenient!

Wealth Therapy at its finest.

We doing 7 cities in 7 days, and it’s bigger than talking stocks or credit.

It’s about building & saving ourselves because no one else is gonna do it.

•

WALLSTREET LOOKS LIKE US NOW!!

node.text:
Let Me Start by saying i totally understand everything that comes with being in the streets.
•

I’ve been shot, i went to prison for 10 years on attempt murder/armored robbery. I’ve been found not guilty & had another charged over turned by supreme court.
•

Had my first crack house at 15, had my crack hiuse ran in at 16.. There isn’t one part of the game i don’t know or relate too.
•

We know that there’s no winning that game. Yea you’ll have major D.R.I.P
•

You’ll get a dope whip, you’ll take care of the fam for a few. & You’ll get some of the baddest females (that comes with the game)
•

But very few retire from the game successfully & at that point, the same people we are attempting to provide for now don’t have us!
•

Only a few of the day 1’s gone stay with you that entire bid & theyll remember you occasionally when you’re in the grave.
•

And it’s not becuase they not loyal, it’s just because they are also figuring out their life.
•

Stop tryna make a million in the streets. Take the street money & start investing.
•

take that street money & open a business.
•

The streets, the block, the game, none of that shit fine take care our family.
•

And as someone who’s made it out the streets. Mannn there’s no better joy than spending time with my lil one every day & not looking over my shoulders.
•

I’m enjoying birthdays, holidays & random free days where i just say let’s go to Disney!
•

I can’t tell you get out the streets, but know that music, and entertainment lies to us.
•

The real gangstas are in the stock market, in real estate, have trucking companies o running businesses going home to their families, creating generational wealth.
•

ITS A NEW DAY FAMILY… They getting wealthy locking us up & burying us.
•

BIG HOMIE TRAP!!!!

So yesterday I didn’t look any of my investing accounts at because I knew the market was taking a serious hit, so i didn’t need that type of negative energy in my life lol
•

Even though it was only a 2.7% decline, I know certain stocks were bleeding dramatically.
•

On days like that, I just turn the App off.
•

I saw the market bounced back this morning, so I said let me take a peek.
•

And today we did 97k…. Now, honestly between last week & yesterday I’m  recovering some of those gains back.
•

This is why you don’t sell when the market Declines, either you buy more, or you do nothing.
•

Had I sold, I would have locked in those losses.
•

So this is the market printing more money to give me what it took from me lol.
•

I will say, when you play the buy and hold game, the market will give more than it takes from you.
•

I can educate you on a lot of things, but I can’t teach you how to emotionally deal with how you’ll feel when the market declines.
•

check out my 4 ebook deal by dm me the word “KILO”
•

Dm me the word “Trapper” to get 1 week free in Trappers Anonymous

Or, get 12 hours of game from my 2 day workshop for $99 & get the reply by dm me the word “WORKSHOP”

This won’t be the last time the market drops & bounces back. You just gotta stick to your game plan to be great.
